  "readme": "# @javiportillo/hackerman\n\nHackerman theme port based on the **Hackerman Theme for Visual Studio Code** theme by **Marcos Coimbra**.\n\n*A neon hacker-style color theme* for your pi coding agent.\n\n## Install\n\n```shell\npi install npm:@javiportillo/pi-hackerman\n```\n\nOr try without installing\n\n```shell\npi -e npm:@javiportillo/pi-hackerman\n```\n\nThen select a theme via `/settings`\n\n## Uninstall\n\n```shell\npi remove @javiportillo/pi-hackerman\n```\n\n",
